          <strong>About:</strong> Dirk Ziff is one of the heirs to the Ziff Davis media fortune but carved his path in private equity and sports ventures. He manages the Ziff family’s investments, focusing on sustainable tech and innovative startups. His influence quietly stretches across tech, media, and venture capital. Ziff’s low-key demeanor belies his role as a power broker in Silicon Valley.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">
